== 發行 ==
2011年8月31日，電影以[[第68屆威尼斯電影節|第68屆威尼斯電影節]]的開幕片的身分首映<ref>{{cite news |last=Vivarelli |first=Nick |date=2011-06-22 |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118038944 |title=Venice confirms 'Ides' as opener |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |publisher={{link-en|Reed Business Information|Reed Business Information}} |accessdate=2011-06-22 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/61nplpyV9?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118038944 |archivedate=2011-09-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影視娛樂]]僅購買了美國的發行權，於是由Alliance Films負責加拿大的發行。索尼希望克魯尼保持戲劇的頭銜，但《選戰風雲》已經定稿<ref name="/Film">{{cite news |last=Fischer |first=Russ |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/sony-picks-george-clooneys-the-ides-march-late-2011-oscarquliafying-run |title=Sony Picks up George Clooney's 'The Ides of March' For December 2011 Release |work={{link-en|/Film|/Film}} |date=2010-11-02 |accessdate=2011-03-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/61npzGqRp?url=http://www.slashfilm.com/sony-picks-george-clooneys-the-ides-march-late-2011-oscarquliafying-run |archivedate=2011-09-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。電影原本預定於2011年12月進行有限上映，2012年1月廣泛發行<ref name="/Film">{{cite news |last=Fischer |first=Russ |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/sony-picks-george-clooneys-the-ides-march-late-2011-oscarquliafying-run |title=Sony Picks up George Clooney's 'The Ides of March' For December 2011 Release |work={{link-en|/Film|/Film}} |date=2010-11-02 |accessdate=2011-03-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/61npzGqRp?url=http://www.slashfilm.com/sony-picks-george-clooneys-the-ides-march-late-2011-oscarquliafying-run |archivedate=2011-09-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。然而，索尼最終將電影的上映日期推遲到2011年10月14日<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sony-sets-release-date-george-164016 |title=Sony Sets Release Date for George Clooney's 'The Ides of March' |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]] |date=2011-03-03 |accessdate=2011-04-11 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/61npfnUnk?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sony-sets-release-date-george-164016 |archivedate=2011-09-19 |deadurl=no |first=Pamela |last=McClintock }}</ref>，但後來又移動至10月7日。

== 評價 ==
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度84%，基於221條評論，平均分為7.3/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_ides_of_march |title=The Ides of March |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher={{link-en|Flixster|Flixster}} |accessdate=2011-10-30}}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到67分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-ides-of-march |title=The Ides of March Reviews, Ratings, Credits |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2011-10-07}}</ref>，收穫普遍好評。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「B」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2011/10/box-office-real-steel-ides-of-march.html |title=Box Office: 'Real Steel' KOs competition, including George Clooney |last=Kaufman |first=Amy |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=2011-10-09 |accessdate=2011-10-09}}</ref> 。

[[香港|香港]]《[[頭條日報|頭條日報]]》的[[葉念琛|葉念琛]]表示：「喜歡《選戰風雲》，或許就是她承繼了好萊塢政治電影的優良傳統。以選舉為主題，卻又提供了更廣闊的想像空間教人思量。」<ref>[http://blogcity.me/blog/reply_blog_express.asp?f=DW4JZ5CAGU120803&id=369691 選戰風雲] ''頭條日報''. 2012年2月10日.</ref>

